beer.beer_description:
Buckley Street Brown Ale (a simple nod to our local area) is a beer that is fermented a touch lower than our other beers to give it a clean ester profile that lets the balanced malt and hops do the talking. This is a beer for people who appreciate the subtle characteristics of a well made, very drinkable beer. A brown ale you can enjoy on a hot day!
#supportyourlocalbrewery
